full_text: Screened by NARA, 8/7/2023 LIBERTY EQUALITY FRATERNITY Tax Administration H NO. 47220 REPUBLIC OF HAITI Seal Tax Administration 10 Centimes Stamped Paper REPUBLIC OF HAITI Excerpt from the Registers of Birth of the Civil Registry of the Municipality of aint-Louis-du-Nord Receipt #64248 On this day, December seventh, nineteen hundred and forty-four, the 141st Year of Independence, at ten o'clock in the morning; BIRTH CERTIFICATE Before Us, Alexandre Chanoine, Civil Re- of gistrar of the Municipality of Saint-Louis-du-Nord, the undersigned; MARIE-CLENIE Appeared citizen Charles Gabriel, of age, born property owner, domiciled in this city; Nov.29, 1944 Who presented to us a female child whom he declaredwas born in his domicile on November twenty- Legitimate ninth of this year at ten o'clock in the morning, the Child legitimate issue of his marriage to Elisabeth Merc√©desse, his wife, to which child he has given the Christian names MARIE-CLENIE No. 70 This instrument was executed in our office Baptized in the presence of citizens Philippe Latout and Merzius Jan. 25, 1945 Louistoas, of age, property owners, domiciled in this at Saint- municipality, who, having read the same, signed.
